playlist_videos.title: Mojo Mail | E1 S1 Fun Truck Cartoon for Kids | Mojo Swoptops
playlist_videos.description:
What top would be best for delivering parcels around town? Mojo and Bo need to decide fast and get those parcels delivered, whether it’s by land, water, or high in the air! Find out what happens in the FIRST full episode of Mojo Swoptops!

#mojoswoptops #truck #cartoon #mojo #swoptops #animation #kindergarten #preschool #trucksforkids

***

Mojo Swoptops is the little truck that swops its top. A brand new animated series for kids, Mojo and Bo (the bestest buds) answer any call for help from the people of Swoppiton and always (well almost always) save the day! Join us in a brand new adventure, as we swop that top and zoom to the rescue! Let's go go!

To watch Mojo Swoptops in the UK also head over the CBeebies channel and BBC iPlayer. 

To watch Mojo Swoptops full episodes outside the UK, subscribe to the Mojo Swoptops Official channel!

***

Download the brand new Meet Mojo Swoptops app, available on all the app stores (https://www.mojoswoptops.com/grown-ups/apps)!

Head over to MojoSwoptops.com to discover more about your favourite new show!

Mojo and Bo become a high-speed parcel delivery service, but what top is best for the job? Find out what happens in this fun clip from animated series for kids, Mojo Swoptops.

***

#mojoswoptops #truck #cartoon #mojo #swoptops #animation #kindergarten #preschool #trucksforkids

***

Mojo Swoptops is the little truck that swops its top. A brand new animated series for kids, Mojo and Bo (the bestest buds) answer any call for help from the people of Swoppiton and always (well almost always) save the day! Join us in a brand new adventure, as we swop that top and zoom to the rescue! Let's go go!

To watch Mojo Swoptops in the UK also head over the CBeebies channel and BBC iPlayer. 

To watch Mojo Swoptops full episodes outside the UK, subscribe to the Mojo Swoptops Official channel!

***

Download the brand new Meet Mojo Swoptops app, available on all the app stores (https://www.mojoswoptops.com/grown-ups/apps)!

Head over to MojoSwoptops.com to discover more about your favourite new show!
